title: Moe And A Celebrity Passenger Almost Went Down With The Plane!
description:
Did you know that if your plane is in danger mid-flight the pilots HAVE to tell you? @ImMoeMitch found that out this weekend! He'll talk about his flight from hell featuring a secret celebrity guest!
